> It means that static buffer can be used with setvbuf.

This seems to be also true for NextStep 3.2 und OSF/1.  Citing from the
fclose(3) manual-pages:

Next: "Buffers allocated by the standard input/output system are freed"

OSF: "If the associated buffer was automatically allocated, it is
deallocated".

